"This is another direction in our efforts to support enterprises and ensure to arrange dozens of special meetings for them. "
In addition, master classes, cooking contests, as well as Russian food tastings cooked by Russian famous chefs and of the "Exploring Russian Food in Shanghai Station" project will be held at the Expo.
